{{Taxobox | image = | image_caption = | domain = [[Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Planctomycetes]] | classis = [[Planctomycetacia]] | subclassis = | ordo = [[Planctomycetales]] | subordo = | familia = [[Planctomycetaceae]] | genus = '''''Rubripirellula''''' | genus_authority = Bondoso et al. 2016<ref name=Rubripirellula>{{cite journal |last1=Parte |first1=A.C. |title=Rubripirellula |website=www.bacterio.net |url=http://www.bacterio.net/rubripirellula.html}}</ref> | type_species = ''Rubripirellula obstinata''<ref name=Rubripirellula/> | subdivision_ranks = [[Species]] | subdivision = ''[[Rubripirellula obstinata|R. obstinata]]''<ref name=Rubripirellula/> | synonyms = }}
'''''Rubripirellula''''' is a genus of bacteria from the family of [[Planctomycetaceae]] with one known species (''[[Rubripirellula obstinata]]'').<ref name=Rubripirellula/><ref>{{cite journal |title=Rubripirellula |website=www.uniprot.org |url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/1579505 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Parker |first1=Charles Thomas |last2=Garrity |first2=George M |title=Taxonomic Abstract for the genera. |journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts |date=1 January 2003 |doi=10.1601/tx.26307 |language=en}}</ref><ref name=PMID>{{cite journal |last1=Bondoso |first1=J |last2=Albuquerque |first2=L |last3=Nobre |first3=MF |last4=Lobo-da-Cunha |first4=A |last5=da Costa |first5=MS |last6=Lage |first6=OM |title=Roseimaritima ulvae gen. nov., sp. nov. and Rubripirellula obstinata gen. nov., sp. nov. two novel planctomycetes isolated from the epiphytic community of macroalgae. |journal=Systematic and Applied Microbiology |date=February 2015 |volume=38 |issue=1 |pages=8–15 |doi=10.1016/j.syapm.2014.10.004 |pmid=25487949}}</ref> ''Rubripirellula obstinata'' has been isolated from the alga ''[[Laminaria]]'' from the northern coast from [[Porto]] in [[Portugal]].<ref name=PMID/><ref>{{cite journal |title=Details: DSM-26289 |website=www.dsmz.de |url=https://www.dsmz.de/catalogues/details/culture/DSM-26289.html |language=en}}</ref>
